text: Mambetkulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Leninsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 175 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Yermolayevo, 7 km from Bugulchan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Mambetkulovo
